OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775139065
OL,3,C'Hazardous gases' released at school
OL,4,Cas staff advised to attend hospital
OL,6,FBy Nathan Hylands
OL,8,FThree staff members at Coleraine
OL,9,FGrammar School have been advised to
OL,10,Fattend hospital following a chemical
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FFirefighters were called to the scene
OL,14,Fon the Castlerock Road at 4:12PM on
OL,15,FTuesday.
OL,17,FNo pupils were present at the school
OL,18,Fdue to the Easter holidays.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
