PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1775139065
OL,3,C'Hazardous gases' released at school
OL,4,Cas staff advised to attend hospital
OL,6,F"The ambulance, fire and police
OL,7,Fservices attended and the situation is
OL,8,Ffully under control," he added.
OL,10,F"The school is working proactively
OL,11,Fwith the emergency services to ensure
OL,12,Fa full clean-up takes place as soon as
OL,13,Fpossible."
